A <a href="/wiki/Persian_language" title="Persian language">Persian</a> manuscript from the 15th century describing the constructing of <a href="/w/index.php?title=Al-Khornaq&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Al-Khornaq (page does not exist)">Al-Khornaq</a> castle in Al-Hira, the <a href="/wiki/Lakhmids" title="Lakhmids">Lakhmids</a> capital city, miniature painting by <a href="/wiki/Kamal-ud-din_Bihzad" title="Kamal-ud-din Bihzad" class="mw-redirect">Behzad</a></div>
