<p><b>Al Hīra</b> (<a href="/wiki/Arabic" title="Arabic" class="mw-redirect">Arabic</a>: الحيرة) was an ancient city located south of <a href="/wiki/Al-Kufah" title="Al-Kufah" class="mw-redirect">al-Kufah</a> in south-central <a href="/wiki/Iraq" title="Iraq">Iraq</a>.</p>
<p></p>
